    {
        "content": "<p>How can I close the <code>sorry</code>s in the following:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">data.equiv.basic</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">Î¹</span> <span class=\"n\">Î¹'</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Ïƒ</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Î¹</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰ƒ</span> <span class=\"n\">Î¹'</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Î±</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Î¹</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Î±'</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Î¹'</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">e</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">âˆ€</span> <span class=\"o\">â¦ƒ</span><span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"o\">â¦„,</span> <span class=\"n\">Ïƒ</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">j</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰ƒ</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±'</span> <span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">Î </span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰ƒ</span> <span class=\"bp\">Î </span> <span class=\"n\">i'</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">Î±'</span> <span class=\"n\">i'</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">to_fun</span>    <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"bp\">Î»</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">i'</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">e</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Ïƒ.apply_symm_apply</span> <span class=\"n\">i'</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"n\">Ïƒ.symm</span> <span class=\"n\">i'</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">inv_fun</span>   <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"bp\">Î»</span> <span class=\"n\">F</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">e</span> <span class=\"n\">rfl</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">symm</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"n\">F</span> <span class=\"bp\">$</span> <span class=\"n\">Ïƒ</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">left_inv</span>  <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"bp\">Î»</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">ext</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">simp</span> <span class=\"n\">only</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">},</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- stuck because `Î± i` is different type to `Î± (Ïƒ.symm (Ïƒ i))`</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">right_inv</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"gr\">sorry</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
